00:54:17,961 --> 00:54:18,681
Huh?

644
00:54:18,680 --> 00:54:20,120
Yvonne, exactly.

645
00:54:20,120 --> 00:54:25,881
So now we're switching to Yvonne and masochistic martyrdom as a parody of crucifixion.

646
00:54:25,881 --> 00:54:27,641
That's what's going to happen there.

647
00:54:27,640 --> 00:54:31,080
But it's still, it's very tightly related to crucifixion.

648
00:54:31,080 --> 00:54:33,641
It's just our wrong way to do it.

649
00:54:34,600 --> 00:54:36,120
Oh, now here's the funny thing.

