00:55:02,921 --> 00:55:10,961
I don't know whether I found this or somebody else found this, but I always thought it's one of the funniest little things that Dostoevsky's tucked in here.

657
00:55:07,640 --> 00:55:14,640
Okay, on 257, that first full paragraph.

658
00:55:14,961 --> 00:55:25,841
They've just been talking about rebellion and Yvonne's despair that he's going to commit suicide later, age of 30.

