00:55:25,841 --> 00:55:29,920
And now Yvonne turned suddenly and went his way without looking back.

660
00:55:29,921 --> 00:55:34,801
It was just as Dmitri had left Alyasha the day before, though the parting had been very different.

661
00:55:34,801 --> 00:55:38,000
So now we get Yvonne and Dmitry associated.

662
00:55:38,000 --> 00:55:44,641
The strange resemblance flashed like an arrow through Alyasha's mind in the distress and rejection of that moment.

