715
01:00:43,721 --> 01:00:48,041
They just go out and eat lots of ugly things, living on locusts and roots.

716
01:00:48,040 --> 01:00:56,280
And thou mayest indeed point with pride at those children of freedom, of free love, of free and splendid sacrifice in thy name, and so forth.

717
01:00:56,281 --> 01:01:01,480
Well, that's the wrong view clearly presented by Yvonne.

718
01:01:01,480 --> 01:01:03,000
He sees it in Katerina.

719
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:04,760
He sees it in the Grand Inquisitor.

720
01:01:04,761 --> 01:01:07,081
And now we've got to see it in him.

721
01:01:07,080 --> 01:01:16,681
So on 569, it's all got to do with his sense of involvement in the murder.

722
01:01:25,640 --> 01:01:32,600
About 10 lines down, Alyasha is telling him, I only know one thing, Alyasha went on, still almost in a whisper.

723
01:01:32,600 --> 01:01:34,601
It wasn't you killed father.

724
01:01:34,600 --> 01:01:36,200
What do you mean, not you?

725
01:01:36,200 --> 01:01:37,881
Yvonne was thunderstruck.

726
01:01:37,881 --> 01:01:41,160
It was not you who killed father, not you, Alyasha repeated.

727
01:01:41,801 --> 01:01:44,281
The silence lasted for half a minute.

728
01:01:44,281 --> 01:01:45,401
I know I didn't.

729
01:01:45,401 --> 01:01:46,200
Are you raving?

730
01:01:46,200 --> 01:01:48,601
said Yvonne, with a pale, distorted smile.

731
01:01:48,600 --> 01:01:50,361
His eyes were riveted on Alyasha.

732
01:01:50,361 --> 01:01:52,281
They were standing under a lamppost.

733
01:01:52,281 --> 01:01:56,600
No, Yvonne, you told yourself several times that you're the murderer.

734
01:01:56,601 --> 01:02:00,601
And there's something else.

735
01:02:00,601 --> 01:02:01,320
Let's see.

736
01:02:01,481 --> 01:02:02,680
Let me skip a little.

737
01:02:03,000 --> 01:02:09,280
He was speaking now, as it were, not of himself, not of his own will, but obeying some irresistible command.

738
01:02:07,881 --> 01:02:14,801
You have accused yourself and have confessed to yourself that you are the murderer and no one else, that you didn't do it.

739
01:02:15,120 --> 01:02:16,000
You're mistaken.

740
01:02:16,000 --> 01:02:16,961
You are not the murderer.

741
01:02:16,961 --> 01:02:17,520
Do you hear?

742
01:02:17,521 --> 01:02:18,560
It was not you.

743
01:02:18,561 --> 01:02:20,640
God has sent me to tell you.

744
01:02:20,881 --> 01:02:35,520
Where God always means, I think, just the connectedness, the power of the true connectedness is what makes Alyaka able to see these things and say these things that other people can't see and say.

745
01:02:41,921 --> 01:02:53,680
And after that, Yvonne, who you know can't ever face anybody who sees anything wrong with him, and he thinks, it's so weird, I realize.

746
01:02:53,681 --> 01:03:02,560
Yvonne wants to take on the crime just to show that he's better than anybody else because he at least admits that he did it.

747
01:03:02,801 --> 01:03:06,881
And so Alyasha is sort of throwing cold water on this plan of Yvonne.

748
01:03:06,961 --> 01:03:22,160
So at the top of 570, in the second paragraph, as soon as Alyasha's told him this, he says, Alyasha, he said with a cold smile, I can't endure prophets and epileptics, messengers from God especially, and you know that only too well.

749
01:03:22,160 --> 01:03:24,240
I don't want to see you again from this moment on.

